---
const title = "Pour ma famille — l'aventure de Papa";
const description = "Un carnet d'aventure illustré pour ma famille — le projet openswissdata, la chasse aux trésors et la tirelire qui se remplit.";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Caveat:wght@500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- ╭──────────────────────────────────────────╮
         │  PAPER BACKGROUND (texture + corners)    │
         ╰──────────────────────────────────────────╯ -->
    <div class="paper-bg" aria-hidden>
      <div class="paper-grain"></div>
      <div class="paper-margin paper-margin-left"></div>
      <div class="paper-margin paper-margin-right"></div>
      <div class="paper-corner corner-tl"></div>
      <div class="paper-corner corner-tr"></div>
      <div class="paper-corner corner-bl"></div>
      <div class="paper-corner corner-br"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- ╭──────────────────────────────────────────╮
         │  HERO — la couverture du carnet          │
         ╰──────────────────────────────────────────╯ -->
    <section class="cover">
      <div class="stamp stamp-tilt">
        <span class="stamp-line">CARNET DE BORD</span>
        <span class="stamp-line stamp-big">CHAPITRE 1</span>
        <span class="stamp-line">PRINTEMPS 2026</span>
      </div>

      <div class="cover-eyebrow">✚ Pour ma famille — un carnet d'aventure</div>

      <h1 class="cover-title">
        L'<span class="word-emph">aventure</span> de Papa,<br />
        <span class="word-script">racontée comme une histoire.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="cover-lede">
        Bonjour. Je m'appelle Alain. Voilà ce que je fabrique chaque soir,<br />
        pourquoi j'y crois, et comment ça pourrait nous rapporter de l'argent.
      </p>

      <!-- Hero illustration : Papa + 3 coffres -->
      <div class="cover-illu">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 720 360" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" aria-label="Papa devant trois coffres">
          <!-- Sky -->
          <rect x="0" y="0" width="720" height="280" fill="#EAF3FB"/>
          <!-- Mountains -->
          <path d="M0 280 L80 200 L120 230 L200 140 L260 200 L340 130 L420 210 L500 150 L600 220 L680 170 L720 220 L720 280 Z" fill="#B0CFD9" opacity="0.5"/>
          <path d="M0 280 L100 220 L180 250 L280 180 L380 240 L470 200 L580 250 L660 220 L720 240 L720 280 Z" fill="#7DA8B5" opacity="0.6"/>
          <!-- Grass -->
          <rect x="0" y="280" width="720" height="80" fill="#C5DD9C"/>
          <ellipse cx="120" cy="320" rx="180" ry="14" fill="#A4C476" opacity="0.6"/>
          <ellipse cx="500" cy="335" rx="240" ry="14" fill="#A4C476" opacity="0.6"/>

          <!-- Sun -->
          <circle cx="600" cy="80" r="36" fill="#F5C63E"/>
          <g stroke="#F5C63E" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round">
            <line x1="600" y1="20" x2="600" y2="35"/>
            <line x1="540" y1="80" x2="555" y2="80"/>
            <line x1="660" y1="80" x2="645" y2="80"/>
            <line x1="558" y1="40" x2="568" y2="50"/>
            <line x1="642" y1="40" x2="632" y2="50"/>
          </g>

          <!-- Cloud -->
          <g fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.85">
            <ellipse cx="200" cy="80" rx="38" ry="18"/>
            <ellipse cx="230" cy="68" rx="28" ry="16"/>
            <ellipse cx="170" cy="74" rx="22" ry="14"/>
          </g>

          <!-- Papa (stick figure, casquette, clé) -->
          <g class="papa">
            <!-- chapeau -->
            <path d="M270 120 L320 120 L325 110 L265 110 Z" fill="#DC1F2D"/>
            <rect x="262" y="118" width="66" height="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <circle cx="295" cy="105" r="4" fill="#FFFFFF"/>
            <!-- tête -->
            <circle cx="295" cy="145" r="22" fill="#F5D6B0"/>
            <!-- yeux -->
            <circle cx="288" cy="142" r="2" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <circle cx="302" cy="142" r="2" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <!-- sourire -->
            <path d="M286 152 Q295 158 304 152" stroke="#1F1A14" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- corps -->
            <rect x="278" y="167" width="34" height="50" rx="4" fill="#5B9BD5"/>
            <!-- bras gauche (avec clé) -->
            <line x1="278" y1="180" x2="248" y2="208" stroke="#F5D6B0" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- clé -->
            <g transform="translate(232 200) rotate(20)">
              <circle cx="6" cy="6" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#D9A648" stroke-width="3"/>
              <circle cx="6" cy="6" r="2" fill="#FBF7EE"/>
              <rect x="11" y="4" width="22" height="4" fill="#D9A648"/>
              <rect x="26" y="4" width="3" height="9" fill="#D9A648"/>
              <rect x="31" y="4" width="3" height="6" fill="#D9A648"/>
            </g>
            <!-- bras droit -->
            <line x1="312" y1="180" x2="332" y2="200" stroke="#F5D6B0" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- jambes -->
            <line x1="288" y1="217" x2="280" y2="265" stroke="#1F1A14" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="302" y1="217" x2="312" y2="265" stroke="#1F1A14" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <!-- chaussures -->
            <ellipse cx="278" cy="270" rx="10" ry="4" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <ellipse cx="314" cy="270" rx="10" ry="4" fill="#1F1A14"/>
          </g>

          <!-- Coffre 1 -->
          <g class="chest chest-1" transform="translate(380 220)">
            <rect x="0" y="20" width="80" height="48" rx="4" fill="#8B5E2A"/>
            <path d="M0 24 Q40 -10 80 24 L80 30 L0 30 Z" fill="#A6712F"/>
            <rect x="35" y="40" width="10" height="14" fill="#D9A648"/>
            <circle cx="40" cy="44" r="2" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="30" x2="80" y2="30" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </g>
          <text x="420" y="298" text-anchor="middle" class="chest-label">TARES</text>

          <!-- Coffre 2 -->
          <g class="chest chest-2" transform="translate(490 215)">
            <rect x="0" y="20" width="80" height="48" rx="4" fill="#8B5E2A"/>
            <path d="M0 24 Q40 -10 80 24 L80 30 L0 30 Z" fill="#A6712F"/>
            <rect x="35" y="40" width="10" height="14" fill="#D9A648"/>
            <circle cx="40" cy="44" r="2" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="30" x2="80" y2="30" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </g>
          <text x="530" y="293" text-anchor="middle" class="chest-label">NOGA</text>

          <!-- Coffre 3 -->
          <g class="chest chest-3" transform="translate(600 222)">
            <rect x="0" y="20" width="80" height="48" rx="4" fill="#8B5E2A"/>
            <path d="M0 24 Q40 -10 80 24 L80 30 L0 30 Z" fill="#A6712F"/>
            <rect x="35" y="40" width="10" height="14" fill="#D9A648"/>
            <circle cx="40" cy="44" r="2" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="30" x2="80" y2="30" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          </g>
          <text x="640" y="300" text-anchor="middle" class="chest-label">FINMA</text>

          <!-- Texte décoratif -->
          <text x="380" y="190" class="hero-arrow-text" transform="rotate(-8 380 190)">trois trésors à débloquer →</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <p class="cover-signature">— Alain, le 30 avril 2026</p>

      <a href="#chapter-2" class="scroll-cue">
        Tourner la page
        <svg width="14" height="22" viewBox="0 0 14 22" fill="none">
          <path d="M7 1 V19 M2 14 L7 19 L12 14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- ╭──────────────────────────────────────────╮
         │  CH 2 — LE PROBLÈME                      │
         ╰──────────────────────────────────────────╯ -->
    <section class="chapter" id="chapter-2">
      <div class="chapter-num">Chapitre 2</div>
      <h2 class="chapter-title">
        Les coffres de l'État sont <em>verrouillés</em>.
      </h2>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          La Suisse a des <strong>coffres pleins de données précieuses</strong>. Le tarif douanier
          (TARES), la liste des banques agréées (FINMA), les classifications des entreprises
          (NOGA) — tout est là.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mais quand on les ouvre, on tombe sur ça :
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3 coffres ouverts montrant des PDFs froissés -->
      <div class="problem-chests">
        <div class="problem-chest">
          <div class="problem-chest-illu">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" aria-hidden>
              <!-- coffre ouvert -->
              <g transform="translate(40 60)">
                <path d="M0 30 Q60 -25 120 30 L120 80 L0 80 Z" fill="#A6712F" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M0 35 L120 35" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
                <rect x="50" y="50" width="20" height="20" fill="#D9A648"/>
                <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="3" fill="#1F1A14"/>
              </g>
              <!-- PDFs froissés qui sortent -->
              <g class="messy-paper" transform="translate(70 30)">
                <path d="M0 0 L40 -5 L42 25 L8 30 L4 22 L-3 18 Z" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="35" y2="3" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="6" y1="12" x2="32" y2="9" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="28" y2="16" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="22" y="-12" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka" font-size="10" fill="#DC1F2D" font-weight="600">PDF</text>
              </g>
              <g class="messy-paper-2" transform="translate(110 50)">
                <path d="M0 0 L36 4 L34 32 L4 28 Z" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <line x1="5" y1="8" x2="30" y2="11" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="5" y1="14" x2="28" y2="17" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="20" y="-8" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka" font-size="9" fill="#DC1F2D" font-weight="600">XLS cassé</text>
              </g>
              <!-- ZZZ confusion -->
              <text x="40" y="35" font-family="Caveat" font-size="22" fill="#8A8D95">!?</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>2&nbsp;400 pages de PDF</h3>
          <p>Le tarif douanier suisse complet. En PDF. Bonne chance pour le brancher dans un logiciel.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="problem-chest">
          <div class="problem-chest-illu">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" aria-hidden>
              <g transform="translate(40 60)">
                <path d="M0 30 Q60 -25 120 30 L120 80 L0 80 Z" fill="#A6712F" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M0 35 L120 35" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
                <rect x="50" y="50" width="20" height="20" fill="#D9A648"/>
              </g>
              <!-- Caractères cassés -->
              <g transform="translate(60 30)">
                <rect x="0" y="0" width="80" height="50" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5" rx="3"/>
                <text x="6" y="14" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#1F1A14">M&#252;ller</text>
                <text x="6" y="26" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#DC1F2D">M??ller</text>
                <text x="6" y="38" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#DC1F2D">M&Atilde;&frac14;ller</text>
                <text x="40" y="50" font-family="Caveat" font-size="14" fill="#DC1F2D">??!</text>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Encodage cassé</h3>
          <p>Les noms suisses (Müller, Genève, Zürich) deviennent illisibles. C'est un fichier des années 90.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="problem-chest">
          <div class="problem-chest-illu">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" aria-hidden>
              <g transform="translate(40 60)">
                <path d="M0 30 Q60 -25 120 30 L120 80 L0 80 Z" fill="#A6712F" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="2"/>
                <path d="M0 35 L120 35" stroke="#5C3F1D" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
                <rect x="50" y="50" width="20" height="20" fill="#D9A648"/>
              </g>
              <!-- 10 listes éparpillées -->
              <g class="scattered" transform="translate(50 30)">
                <rect x="0" y="0" width="20" height="26" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5" rx="2" transform="rotate(-12 10 13)"/>
                <rect x="22" y="-2" width="20" height="26" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5" rx="2" transform="rotate(8 32 11)"/>
                <rect x="46" y="2" width="20" height="26" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5" rx="2" transform="rotate(-5 56 15)"/>
                <rect x="70" y="-3" width="20" height="26" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5" rx="2" transform="rotate(15 80 10)"/>
                <rect x="94" y="2" width="20" height="26" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5" rx="2" transform="rotate(-8 104 15)"/>
                <text x="60" y="-10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Caveat" font-size="20" fill="#DC1F2D">×10</text>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>10 listes différentes</h3>
          <p>Les banques agréées ? Réparties sur 10 pages web différentes. Aucune liste unifiée.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="aside aside-red">
        <span class="aside-mark">!</span>
        Résultat&nbsp;: <strong>personne ne les utilise</strong>. Les comptables font des copier-coller à la main.
        Les banques refont le travail dans leur coin. Une montagne d'heures perdues, partout en Suisse.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ╭──────────────────────────────────────────╮
         │  CH 3 — L'ATELIER                        │
         ╰──────────────────────────────────────────╯ -->
    <section class="chapter chapter-shaded">
      <div class="chapter-num">Chapitre 3</div>
      <h2 class="chapter-title">
        Alors j'ai construit une <em>machine</em>.
      </h2>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Une machine qui prend les fichiers cassés et les remet en ordre. Qui corrige les
          encodages, qui assemble les 10 listes en une seule, qui transforme le PDF de
          2&nbsp;400 pages en tableau bien rangé.
        </p>
        <p class="prose-handwritten">
          Ce n'est pas magique. C'est juste très ennuyeux.<br />
          Ça prend des semaines. <strong>C'est précisément pour ça que personne d'autre ne le fait.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Machine illustration -->
      <div class="workshop">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 720 320" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" aria-label="Machine de transformation">
          <!-- Tapis roulant entrée -->
          <rect x="20" y="180" width="180" height="14" fill="#5C3F1D" rx="2"/>
          <g class="conveyor-belts">
            <circle cx="40" cy="187" r="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <circle cx="80" cy="187" r="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <circle cx="120" cy="187" r="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <circle cx="160" cy="187" r="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
          </g>

          <!-- PDF moche entrant -->
          <g class="enter-paper">
            <rect x="0" y="0" width="40" height="50" rx="3" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#8A8D95" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="10" x2="34" y2="10" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="30" y2="18" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="26" x2="34" y2="26" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="34" x2="28" y2="34" stroke="#C5C9D2" stroke-width="1"/>
            <text x="20" y="60" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka" font-size="10" fill="#DC1F2D" font-weight="600">PDF</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Machine -->
          <g>
            <rect x="220" y="100" width="280" height="140" rx="14" fill="#DC1F2D"/>
            <rect x="220" y="100" width="280" height="140" rx="14" fill="none" stroke="#9E1620" stroke-width="3"/>
            <rect x="240" y="120" width="240" height="100" rx="8" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <!-- écran -->
            <text x="360" y="155" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka" font-size="14" fill="#7DDB7D" font-weight="600">openswissdata</text>
            <text x="360" y="178" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="11" fill="#7DDB7D">[ nettoyage en cours ]</text>
            <text x="360" y="200" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="11" fill="#7DDB7D">7 511 lignes ✓</text>
            <!-- diodes animées -->
            <circle cx="248" cy="118" r="3" fill="#7DDB7D" class="led led-1"/>
            <circle cx="262" cy="118" r="3" fill="#F5C63E" class="led led-2"/>
            <circle cx="276" cy="118" r="3" fill="#7DDB7D" class="led led-3"/>
            <!-- entonnoir -->
            <path d="M210 110 L 230 130 L 230 150 L 210 130 Z" fill="#9E1620"/>
            <path d="M210 110 L 200 110 L 200 130 L 210 130 Z" fill="#7A1019"/>
            <!-- sortie -->
            <path d="M510 130 L530 130 L530 150 L510 150 Z" fill="#9E1620"/>
            <!-- vapeur -->
            <g class="steam">
              <circle cx="300" cy="100" r="6" fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.7"/>
              <circle cx="320" cy="92" r="5" fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.5"/>
              <circle cx="350" cy="86" r="7" fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.6"/>
              <circle cx="380" cy="92" r="5" fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.5"/>
              <circle cx="410" cy="98" r="6" fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.4"/>
            </g>
            <!-- antenne -->
            <line x1="360" y1="100" x2="360" y2="80" stroke="#1F1A14" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="360" cy="76" r="4" fill="#F5C63E"/>
            <!-- pieds -->
            <rect x="240" y="240" width="20" height="20" fill="#7A1019"/>
            <rect x="460" y="240" width="20" height="20" fill="#7A1019"/>
          </g>

          <!-- Tapis roulant sortie -->
          <rect x="520" y="180" width="180" height="14" fill="#5C3F1D" rx="2"/>
          <g class="conveyor-belts">
            <circle cx="540" cy="187" r="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <circle cx="580" cy="187" r="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <circle cx="620" cy="187" r="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
            <circle cx="660" cy="187" r="6" fill="#1F1A14"/>
          </g>

          <!-- Boîtes propres en sortie -->
          <g class="exit-box exit-box-1" transform="translate(540 140)">
            <rect x="0" y="0" width="42" height="32" rx="3" fill="#5B9BD5"/>
            <text x="21" y="20" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka" font-size="11" fill="#FFFFFF" font-weight="700">JSON</text>
          </g>
          <g class="exit-box exit-box-2" transform="translate(595 140)">
            <rect x="0" y="0" width="50" height="32" rx="3" fill="#6FAE5E"/>
            <text x="25" y="20" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka" font-size="11" fill="#FFFFFF" font-weight="700">PARQUET</text>
          </g>
          <g class="exit-box exit-box-3" transform="translate(660 140)">
            <rect x="0" y="0" width="34" height="32" rx="3" fill="#D9A648"/>
            <text x="17" y="20" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka" font-size="11" fill="#FFFFFF" font-weight="700">SQL</text>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          De l'autre côté, je sors des fichiers <strong>propres, vérifiés, prêts à brancher</strong>.
          Trois formats au choix selon ce dont le client a besoin&nbsp;:
        </p>
        <ul class="bullet-list">
          <li><strong>JSON</strong> — comprenez "format universel des sites web et applications".</li>
          <li><strong>Parquet</strong> — pour les analystes qui font des graphiques.</li>
          <li><strong>SQL</strong> — pour ceux qui ont une base de données.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Et chaque trimestre, je relance la machine pour que les fichiers restent à jour.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ╭──────────────────────────────────────────╮
         │  CH 4 — LES TRÉSORS                      │
         ╰──────────────────────────────────────────╯ -->
    <section class="chapter">
      <div class="chapter-num">Chapitre 4</div>
      <h2 class="chapter-title">
        Trois trésors à <em>vendre</em>. Et un coffret qui contient les trois.
      </h2>

      <div class="treasures">
        <div class="treasure">
          <div class="treasure-emoji">🚂</div>
          <div class="treasure-tag">Trésor n°1 · Douanes</div>
          <h3>TARES</h3>
          <p>Le tarif douanier suisse complet. Pour quoi&nbsp;? Pour calculer les taxes à l'import/export.</p>
          <div class="treasure-stats">
            <div><span class="stat-num">7&nbsp;511</span><span class="stat-lab">codes douaniers</span></div>
            <div><span class="stat-num">~&nbsp;40&nbsp;h</span><span class="stat-lab">économisées par client</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="treasure-price">
            <span class="price-amt">299 CHF</span>
            <span class="price-sub">une fois · ou 120 CHF/an pour les mises à jour</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="treasure">
          <div class="treasure-emoji">📊</div>
          <div class="treasure-tag">Trésor n°2 · Économie</div>
          <h3>NOGA + NACE + ISIC</h3>
